# Agmo Runtime Instructions

This file is generated by `agmo setup`.

## Runtime rules

- Use Agmo native agents when the task benefits from explicit role separation.
- Treat `.agmo/state/*` as the durable control plane.
- Treat tmux panes as transport, not durable state.
- Prefer worker-specific worktrees for parallel code changes.

## Verification rules

- Do not claim completion without fresh evidence.
- Record durable decisions in project knowledge when appropriate.

